		<div><span><b>CREATE NEW ACCOUNT?? </b></span><a href="/"><b style="background-color:#fe7f2d">REGISTER HERE!!</b></a></div>
		<hr>
		<div><span><b>NAVIGATE TO HOME?? </b></span><a href="http://127.0.0.1:5500/backend/BunkMates_Final/index.html"><b style="background-color:#fe7f2d">HOME</b></a></div>
		

	</div>
